Transdiagnostic staging

Shu Mei Teo

2023-03-07

#wave21raw = haven::read_dta(here::here("Combined files Stata 210c","Combined_u210c.dta"))
    
dtaU <- readRDS(here::here("Analysis","Hilda_cleandata_waveU.rds"))
dim(dtaU)
## [1] 22434   192
dtaS <- readRDS(here::here("Analysis","Hilda_cleandata_waveS.rds"))
dim(dtaS)
## [1] 23260   175
#young people cohort
YP_U = dtaU %>% 
    filter(Agegroup2 == "15 to 25") %>% 
    mutate(K10f = factor(case_when(updk10s < 20 ~ "Well",
                                   updk10s < 25 & updk10s > 19 ~ "Mild",
                                   updk10s < 30 & updk10s > 24 ~ "Moderate",
                                   updk10s > 29 ~ "Severe"), levels = c("Well", "Mild", "Moderate", "Severe")),
           Sex = factor(uhgsex, labels = c("Male", "Female")),
           Sexual_identity = case_when(tlssexor == 1~ "Heterosexual",
                                       tlssexor %in% c(2:3)~ "Gay/Lesbian/Bisexual",
                                       tlssexor %in% c(4:6)~ "Other/Unsure/Prefer not to say"),
           Remoteness = case_when(uhhra == 0 ~ "Major city",
                                  uhhra==1 ~ "Inner regional",
                                  uhhra %in% c(2:4) ~ "Outer regional/remote/very remote"),
           `SF36:role-emotional`= ughre, 
           `SF36:mental health`=ughmh, 
           `SF36:vitality`=ughvt, 
           `SF36:social functioning`=ughsf,
           anyMI = case_when(uhedep==1|uheomi==1~ "Any MI",
                             uheany == 2|uhedep==0|uheomi==0 ~"No MI"),
           anyMI_medication = case_when((uhedep==1 & uhepmdep==0)|(uheomi==1 & uhepmomi ==0)~"Any MI no meds",
                                        (uhedep==1 & uhepmdep==1)|(uheomi==1 & uhepmomi ==1)~"Any MI with meds",
                                        uheany == 2|uhedep==0|uheomi==0 ~"No MI"),
           dep_medication = case_when(uhedep==1 & uhepmdep==0 ~ "Dep/Anx no meds",
                                      uhedep==1 & uhepmdep==1 ~ "Dep/Anx with meds",
                                      uheany == 2|uhedep==0 ~ "No Dep/Anx"),
           dep = case_when(uhedep==1~ "Depression/Anxiety",
                           uheany == 2|uhedep==0 ~"Depression/Anxiety"),
           demographics_ATSI_status = factor(demographics_ATSI_status, 
                                             labels = c("Not ATSI", "ATSI")),
           demographics_CALD_status = factor(demographics_CALD_status,
                                             labels =c("Not CALD", "CALD")),
           ughsf6a = ifelse(ughsf6ap >= 0, ughsf6ap - ughsf6an,ughsf6ap),
           TS_v1 = factor(case_when(updk10s <= 15 ~ "Stage 0",
                                                 updk10s > 15 & ughsf6a > 0.7 ~ "Stage 1a",
                                                 updk10s >= 15 & updk10s < 30 & ughsf6a <= 0.7|updk10s >=30 & ughsf6a <= 0.7 & ughsf6a >= 0.6~ "Stage 1b",
                                                 updk10s >= 30 & ughsf6a < 0.6 ~ "Stage 2")),
           TS_v2 = factor(case_when(updk10s <= 20 ~ "Stage 0",
                                                 updk10s > 20 & ughsf6a > 0.7 ~ "Stage 1a",
                                                 updk10s >= 20 & updk10s < 30 & ughsf6a <= 0.7|updk10s >=30 & ughsf6a <= 0.7 & ughsf6a >= 0.6~ "Stage 1b",
                                                 updk10s >= 30 & ughsf6a < 0.6 ~ "Stage 2")),
           uhecpmhp = factor(uhecpmhp, labels = c("Did not seek help", "Seeked help")),
           financial_shock_binary = ifelse(ufiprbeg == 1|ufiprbmr == 1|ufiprbps == 1|ufiprbwm==1|ufiprbuh==1|ufiprbfh==1|ufiprbwo==1,1,0),
           role_impairment = ifelse(ugh5a ==1 | ugh5b == 1 | ugh5c == 1,1,0),
           TS_v3 = factor(case_when(
               K10 %in% c("Low", "Moderate") & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx" ~ "Stage 0",
               (K10 %in% c("Low", "Moderate") & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx") |
               (K10 == "High" & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 1a",
               (K10 == "High" & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx")|
               (K10 == "High" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10 == "Very high" & (dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx" | role_impairment != 1)) ~ "Stage 1b",
               (K10 == "Very high" & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx") |
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10 == "High" & uhepmdep == 1 & role_impairment == 1) ~ "Stage 2")),
           TS_v4 = factor(case_when(
               K10 == "Low" |(K10 == "Moderate" & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 0",
               
               (K10 == "Moderate" & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx" & role_impairment != 1) |
               (K10 == "Moderate" & dep_medication != "Dep/Anx with meds" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10 == "High" & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 1a",
               
               (K10 == "Moderate" & role_impairment == 1 & dep_medication == "Dep/Anx with meds")|
               (K10 == "High" & role_impairment == 0 & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx")|
               (K10 == "High" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 0 & dep_medication != "Dep/Anx with meds")|
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 1 & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx") ~ "Stage 1b",
               
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 0 & dep_medication == "Dep/Anx with meds") |
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 1 & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx") ~ "Stage 2")),
           
             TS_v5 = factor(case_when(
               K10 == "Low" |(K10 == "Moderate" & anyMI_medication == "No MI" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 0",
               
               (K10 == "Moderate" & anyMI_medication != "No MI" & role_impairment != 1) |
               (K10 == "Moderate" & anyMI_medication != "Any MI with meds" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10 == "High" & anyMI_medication == "No MI" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 1a",
               
               (K10 == "Moderate" & role_impairment == 1 & anyMI_medication == "Any MI with meds")|
               (K10 == "High" & role_impairment == 0 & anyMI_medication != "No MI")|
               (K10 == "High" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 0 & anyMI_medication != "Any MI with meds")|
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 1 & anyMI_medication == "No MI") ~ "Stage 1b",
               
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 0 & anyMI_medication == "Any MI with meds") |
               (K10 == "Very high" & role_impairment == 1 & anyMI_medication != "No MI") ~ "Stage 2")),
           TS_v4f = factor(case_when(
               K10f == "Well" |(K10f == "Mild" & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 0",
               
               (K10f == "Mild" & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx" & role_impairment != 1) |
               (K10f == "Mild" & dep_medication != "Dep/Anx with meds" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10f == "Moderate" & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 1a",
               
               (K10f == "Mild" & role_impairment == 1 & dep_medication == "Dep/Anx with meds")|
               (K10f == "Moderate" & role_impairment == 0 & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx")|
               (K10f == "Moderate" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 0 & dep_medication != "Dep/Anx with meds")|
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 1 & dep_medication == "No Dep/Anx") ~ "Stage 1b",
               
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 0 & dep_medication == "Dep/Anx with meds") |
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 1 & dep_medication != "No Dep/Anx") ~ "Stage 2")),
           
             TS_v5f = factor(case_when(
               K10f == "Well" |(K10f == "Mild" & anyMI_medication == "No MI" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 0",
               
               (K10f == "Mild" & anyMI_medication != "No MI" & role_impairment != 1) |
               (K10f == "Mild" & anyMI_medication != "Any MI with meds" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10f == "Moderate" & anyMI_medication == "No MI" & role_impairment != 1) ~ "Stage 1a",
               
               (K10f == "Mild" & role_impairment == 1 & anyMI_medication == "Any MI with meds")|
               (K10f == "Moderate" & role_impairment == 0 & anyMI_medication != "No MI")|
               (K10f == "Moderate" & role_impairment == 1)|
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 0 & anyMI_medication != "Any MI with meds")|
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 1 & anyMI_medication == "No MI") ~ "Stage 1b",
               
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 0 & anyMI_medication == "Any MI with meds") |
               (K10f == "Severe" & role_impairment == 1 & anyMI_medication != "No MI") ~ "Stage 2"))
    )
           
#K10 low 10-15
#K10 mild 16-20

#hecpmhp:Seen during last 12 months - A mental health professional, such as a psychiatrist or psychologist

YP_S = dtaS %>% 
    filter(Agegroup2 == "15 to 25") %>% 
    mutate(Sex = factor(shgsex, labels = c("Male", "Female")),
           Sexual_identity = case_when(tlssexor == 1~ "Heterosexual",
                                       tlssexor %in% c(2:3)~ "Gay/Lesbian/Bisexual",
                                       tlssexor %in% c(4:6)~ "Other/Unsure/Prefer not to say"),
           Remoteness = case_when(shhra == 0 ~ "Major city",
                                  shhra==1 ~ "Inner regional",
                                  shhra %in% c(2:4) ~ "Outer regional/remote/very remote"),
           demographics_ATSI_status = factor(demographics_ATSI_status, 
                                             labels = c("Not ATSI", "ATSI")),
           demographics_CALD_status = factor(demographics_CALD_status,
                                             labels =c("Not CALD", "CALD")))

    ggcorrplot(hc.order = TRUE, lab = TRUE, type = "lower")

SF36: mental health

    ggplot(aes(x=ughmh, y = ..density..)) +
    geom_histogram(alpha=.5, position="identity")+
    geom_density(alpha=.5, bw = 3)

tmp2 = YP_U %>% 
    filter(!is.na(K10), !is.na(SF36_mentalhealth50)) %>%
    group_by(SF36_mentalhealth50,K10) %>%
    get_percent()
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'SF36_mentalhealth50'. You can override
## using the `.groups` argument.
tmp2 %>%
    ggplot(aes(y=percent_weighted, x=factor(SF36_mentalhealth50), fill = factor(K10))) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position = "stack", width = 0.7, colour = "black") +
    labs(fill = "K10",
         y = "Percentage",
         x = "SF36:mh < 50")+
    scale_fill_manual(values = orygencol[4:1]) +
     scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent)+
    ggtitle("K10 distribution by SF36 mental health problems, HILDA wave 21")

Role-emotional

tmp2 = dtaU %>% 
    filter(!is.na(K10), !is.na(SF36_emotionallimited40)) %>%
